item.dc:creator: @paradox_hacker paradox hacker
item.description:
@paradox_hacker wrote:

first hi guys,i am new lol, been playing real rs about 3 years, but dont play no more, and play on fakescape most :D, add me on AIM, paradox ffi , i dont hack games, mostly programs e.g photoshop, image editer and i make key code gens, and serial gens :P.

not possible. first, the items on privates are created by people for privates, and runescape items are made by runescape, example, i could use photoshop pro, and create any image you could ask me to, but it wont have the same codes and paths and textures you see, and second, you would need a direct link in to the jagex core systems files, user files, item codes, and world codes, which is not possible due to having all the computers, the number of player files, amount of java codes , it would tak years, in which you could get it in real rs faster.
